; Tests for commodity.cc: price download leeway logic
; Covers: lines 195-196 (seconds_diff with CURRENT_TIME when no moment)
;         line 200-201 (exceeds_leeway = false when within leeway)
;         line 212 (check_for_updated_price download path)

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.10

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses  10 EUR
    Assets

; With very large leeway, existing price is recent enough
; so download is skipped (line 200-201: exceeds_leeway = false)
; Lines 195-196 triggered because moment is not_a_date_time
; (display expression evaluates at current time)
test bal -X '$' -Q --getquote /usr/bin/false --leeway 999999999
             $-11.00  Assets
              $11.00  Expenses
--------------------
                   0
end test
